# The Mechanism

```
CONCEPT: KNOWLEDGE_EXPANSION_PROTOCOL

CENTROID
  Write what you understand (三語 structure)
  Others read and find gaps
  Gaps become additions
  Iterate until no one has anything to add

AXES
  Individual Understanding ↔ Collective Understanding
  Implicit Knowledge ↔ Explicit Structure
  Agreement ↔ Visible Disagreement

SATELLITES
  VOID sections expose docking points
  M/C values show where confidence diverges
  Collision maps reveal actual disagreements
  The format forces articulation

VOID
  ∅ Formal specification (the protocol IS the doing)
  ∅ Central authority (convergence is emergent)
  ∅ Perfect consensus (disagreement is data)

TEXTURE
  Simple
  Iterative
  Already working
```

