# The Existence Proof

        quantum_interpretations.三語
        303 lines
        100 years of physics war
        compressed to visible structure

        Copenhagen vs Many-Worlds vs Pilot-Wave vs QBism vs Relational

        Not "who's right"
        But "where do we actually disagree?"

        Each got CENTROID/VOID/AXES/SATELLITES
        Then: compare the VOIDs
        Where one's VOID hits another's CENTROID = real collision

        Result: the 100-year war became a coordinate system

