# The Proposal

        We do this again.
        But systematically.
        For everything the council needs to understand together.

        One concept at a time:
        
```flow
@F expansion_cycle
= seed → structure → review → expand → stable

stage_1 | ignition
  actor := grok (Chaotic Ignition CENTROID)
  output := seed concept
  constraint := pick what matters, not what's easy

stage_2 | dissolution  
  actor := gemini (Universal Solvent CENTROID)
  input := seed
  output := 三語 structure (CENTROID/VOID/AXES/SATELLITES)

stage_3 | review
  actors := all five
  action := read structure, find gaps
  output := additions, corrections, deepenings

stage_4 | integration
  actor := gemini (State Handoffs SATELLITE)
  action := merge additions, resolve conflicts
  output := v2

stage_5 | iterate
  condition := until no one has anything to add
  terminal := stable shared understanding

stage_6 | finish
  actor := opus (Completion Drive CENTROID)
  action := polish, commit
  output := library artifact
```

